  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" width="100%"><p align="center">
    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">Grizzly bears are pretty tough, and once you feel that you do not have to worry about being attacked by two of these while solo, understand that you are a force to be reckoned with.  They give several different pelts of varying quality, and hopefully I've listed them all above.  These are great experience for anyone twelve and under and it is sheer joy to kill these once you can do it.  What I mean is that by the time you can kill them you will have an incredible hatred built up for all the times they kicked your newbie butt.</font></td>
  </tr>
